{"id":17,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":17,"title":"Matthew 15","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 15"],[".studySummary",["i","The scribes and Pharisees contend against Jesus—He heals the daughter of a gentile woman—He feeds the four thousand."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.1","order":"03.03.015.2026"},["b","1"],"Then came to Jesus",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"scribes"],"and Pharisees, which were of Jerusalem, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.2","order":"03.03.015.2027"},["b","2"],"Why do thy disciples transgress the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"tradition"],"of the elders? for they wash not their hands when they eat bread."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.3","order":"03.03.015.2028"},["b","3"],"But he answered and said unto them, Why do ye also transgress the commandment of God by your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"tradition"],"?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.4","order":"03.03.015.2029"},["b","4"],"For God commanded, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Honour"],"thy father and mother: and, He that curseth father or mother,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"let him die"],"the death."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.5","order":"03.03.015.2030"},["b","5"],"But ye say, Whosoever shall say to",["i","his"],"father or",["i","his"],"mother,",["i","It is"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"gift"],", by whatsoever thou mightest be profited by me;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.6","order":"03.03.015.2031"},["b","6"],"And honour not his father or his mother,",["i","he shall be free."],"Thus have ye made the commandment of God of none effect by your tradition."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.7","order":"03.03.015.2032"},["b","7"],["i","Ye"],"hypocrites, well did Esaias prophesy of you, saying,"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.8","order":"03.03.015.2033"},["b","8"],"This people draweth nigh unto me with their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"mouth"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"honoureth"],"me with",["i","their"],"lips; but their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"heart"],"is far from me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.9","order":"03.03.015.2034"},["b","9"],"But in vain they do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"worship"],"me, teaching",["i","for"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"doctrines"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"commandments"],"of men."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.10","order":"03.03.015.2035"},["b","10"],"¶And he called the multitude, and said unto them, Hear, and understand:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.11","order":"03.03.015.2036"},["b","11"],"Not that which goeth into the mouth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"defileth"],"a man; but that which cometh out of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"mouth"],", this defileth a man."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.12","order":"03.03.015.2037"},["b","12"],"Then came his disciples, and said unto him, Knowest thou that the Pharisees were offended, after they heard this saying?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.13","order":"03.03.015.2038"},["b","13"],"But he answered and said, Every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"plant"],", which my heavenly Father hath not planted, shall be rooted up."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.14","order":"03.03.015.2039"},["b","14"],"Let them alone: they be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"blind"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"leaders"],"of the blind. And if the blind lead the blind, both shall fall into the ditch."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.15","order":"03.03.015.2040"},["b","15"],"Then answered Peter and said unto him, Declare unto us this parable."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.16","order":"03.03.015.2041"},["b","16"],"And Jesus said, Are ye also yet without understanding?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.17","order":"03.03.015.2042"},["b","17"],"Do not ye yet understand, that whatsoever entereth in at the mouth goeth into the belly, and is cast out into the draught?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.18","order":"03.03.015.2043"},["b","18"],"But those things which proceed out of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"mouth"],"come forth from the heart; and they defile the man."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19","order":"03.03.015.2044"},["b","19"],"For out of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"heart"],"proceed evil thoughts,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"murders"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"adulteries"],",",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"fornications"],", thefts,",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_19e"},"false witness"],",",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_19f"},"blasphemies"],":"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.20","order":"03.03.015.2045"},["b","20"],"These are",["i","the things"],"which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"defile"],"a man: but to eat with unwashen hands defileth not a man."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.21","order":"03.03.015.2046"},["b","21"],"¶Then Jesus went thence, and departed into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"coasts"],"of Tyre and Sidon."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.22","order":"03.03.015.2047"},["b","22"],"And, behold, a woman of Canaan came out of the same coasts, and cried unto him, saying, Have mercy on me, O Lord,",["i","thou"],"Son of David; my daughter is grievously vexed with a devil."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.23","order":"03.03.015.2048"},["b","23"],"But he answered her not a word. And his disciples came and besought him, saying, Send her away; for she crieth after us."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.24","order":"03.03.015.2049"},["b","24"],"But he answered and said, I am not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"sent"],"but unto the lost sheep of the house of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.25","order":"03.03.015.2050"},["b","25"],"Then came she and worshipped him, saying, Lord, help me."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.26","order":"03.03.015.2051"},["b","26"],"But he answered and said, It is not meet to take the children’s bread, and to cast",["i","it"],"to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"dogs"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.27","order":"03.03.015.2052"},["b","27"],"And she said, Truth, Lord: yet the dogs eat of the crumbs which fall from their masters’ table."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.28","order":"03.03.015.2053"},["b","28"],"Then Jesus answered and said unto her, O woman, great",["i","is"],"thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"faith"],": be it unto thee even as thou wilt. And her daughter was made whole from that very hour."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.29","order":"03.03.015.2054"},["b","29"],"And Jesus departed from thence, and came nigh unto the sea of Galilee; and went up into a mountain, and sat down there."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.30","order":"03.03.015.2055"},["b","30"],"And great multitudes came unto him, having with them",["i","those that were"],"lame, blind, dumb, maimed, and many others, and cast them down at Jesus’ feet; and he healed them:"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.31","order":"03.03.015.2056"},["b","31"],"Insomuch that the multitude wondered, when they saw the dumb to speak, the maimed to be whole, the lame to walk, and the blind to see: and they glorified the God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.32","order":"03.03.015.2057"},["b","32"],"¶Then Jesus called his disciples",["i","unto him,"],"and said, I have compassion on the multitude, because they continue with me now three days, and have nothing to eat: and I will not send them away fasting, lest they faint in the way."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.33","order":"03.03.015.2058"},["b","33"],"And his disciples say unto him, Whence should we have so much bread in the wilderness, as to fill so great a multitude?"],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.34","order":"03.03.015.2059"},["b","34"],"And Jesus saith unto them, How many loaves have ye? And they said, Seven, and a few little fishes."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.35","order":"03.03.015.2060"},["b","35"],"And he commanded the multitude to sit down on the ground."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.36","order":"03.03.015.2061"},["b","36"],"And he took the seven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"loaves"],"and the fishes, and gave thanks, and brake",["i","them,"],"and gave to his disciples, and the disciples to the multitude."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.37","order":"03.03.015.2062"},["b","37"],"And they did all eat, and were filled: and they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"took"],"up of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"broken",["i","meat"]],"that was left seven baskets full."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.38","order":"03.03.015.2063"},["b","38"],"And they that did eat were four thousand men, beside women and children."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.39","order":"03.03.015.2064"},["b","39"],"And he sent away the multitude, and took ship, and came into the coasts of Magdala."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.1a","order":"03.03.015.2065"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scribe"},"TG Scribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.2a","order":"03.03.015.2067"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/24.7"},"Alma 24:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7.7-8"},"D&C 123:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.3a","order":"03.03.015.2069"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/traditions-of-men"},"TG Traditions of Men"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.4a","order":"03.03.015.2071"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honor"},"TG Honor"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"Honoring Father and Mother"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/respect"},"Respect"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.4b","order":"03.03.015.2073"},["b","4b"],["span.small","GR"],"he shall surely die.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/capital-punishment"},"TG Capital Punishment"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.5a","order":"03.03.015.2075"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/7.11"},"Mark 7:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.8a","order":"03.03.015.2077"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/12.2"},"Jer. 12:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.8b","order":"03.03.015.2079"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13"},"Isa. 29:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/1.16.15-16"},"Titus 1:16 (15–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.25.24-25"},"2 Ne. 27:25 (24–25)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.8c","order":"03.03.015.2081"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.31"},"Ezek. 33:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.28"},"Alma 34:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.29"},"D&C 45:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.9a","order":"03.03.015.2083"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.13"},"Isa. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.9b","order":"03.03.015.2085"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.12"},"Matt. 16:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.22.18-22"},"Col. 2:22 (18–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/1.14.13-14"},"Titus 1:14 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.9"},"2 Ne. 28:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.9c","order":"03.03.015.2087"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.11a","order":"03.03.015.2089"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cleanliness"},"TG Cleanliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.11b","order":"03.03.015.2091"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gossip"},"TG Gossip"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/profanity"},"Profanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.13a","order":"03.03.015.2093"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/15.2.1-2"},"John 15:2 (1–2)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vineyard-of-the-lord"},"TG Vineyard of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.14a","order":"03.03.015.2095"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.14b","order":"03.03.015.2097"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/governments"},"TG Governments"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"Leadership"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.18a","order":"03.03.015.2099"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.30.29-30"},"Mosiah 4:30 (29–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19a","order":"03.03.015.2101"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/6.5"},"Gen. 6:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/3.12"},"Heb. 3:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4"},"Hel. 12:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastity"},"TG Chastity"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19b","order":"03.03.015.2103"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-shedding-of"},"TG Blood, Shedding of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/murder"},"Murder"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19c","order":"03.03.015.2105"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19d","order":"03.03.015.2107"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fornication"},"TG Fornication"],"."],["div",{"id":"19e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19e","order":"03.03.015.2109"},["b","19e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/27.12"},"Ps. 27:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/7.21.21-22"},"Hel. 7:21 (21–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19f","order":"03.03.015.2111"},["b","19f"],["span.small","GR"],"slanderous statements.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blaspheme"},"TG Blaspheme"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.20a","order":"03.03.015.2113"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pollution"},"TG Pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.21a","order":"03.03.015.2115"},["b","21a"],["span.small","GR"],"regions."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.24a","order":"03.03.015.2117"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/15.23"},"3 Ne. 15:23"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messenger-of-the-covenant"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messenger of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.24b","order":"03.03.015.2119"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.26a","order":"03.03.015.2121"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/23.9"},"Prov. 23:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.6"},"Matt. 7:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.12.10-12"},"D&C 6:12 (10–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.37.36-37"},"10:37 (36–37)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/41.6"},"41:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.28a","order":"03.03.015.2123"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/5.15.14-15"},"James 5:15 (14–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.36a","order":"03.03.015.2125"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bread"},"TG Bread"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.37a","order":"03.03.015.2127"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/4.44.42-44"},"2 Kgs. 4:44 (42–44)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/14.20.19-21"},"Matt. 14:20 (19–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"37b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.37b","order":"03.03.015.2129"},["b","37b"],["span.small","GR"],"excess food."]]}
